{"tid":875477,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"黃志陽：短期等內地再救市 24,200點有支持","createTime":"2018-10-25T02:33:31.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-25T03:04:40.000Z","uid":60281,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"ec3f8753801fd4cb3366d98337ef261252ddb20a","tid":875477,"uid":60281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-25T02:33:31.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20181025/58833255\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181025%2F58833255&d=HlapleOAzD3wBg705ZUsmMP%2FddU7lKBqZb2OVh9Tir8%3D&h=1668a54f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181025%2F58833255&h=fcd83788\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20181025/58833255</a><br />\n<br />\n港股創17個月低位，獨立股評人黃志陽表示若港股要有大反彈，若內地政策有刺激，令有短暫反彈，恒指支持位於24,200點。<br />\n<br />\n黃志陽表示，因為目前外圍市況最近轉差，中美關係仍然差，市場也未有好消息，唯一好消息是最近內地A股沽盤開始停，並有明顯反彈，惟若A股走勢仍然差，港股便沒有好消息支持；若A股重回之前低位，且有中央政府「出口術」支持，令市況便有支撐，使港股跌勢減慢。不過，即使有反彈也未必能在短時間內發生，所以投資者需要耐心等待。<br />\n<br />\n他又指港股現時明顯踏入熊市，反覆向下，投資者偶爾可博熊市反彈，因為當恒指跌得深或在大跌的日子的昔日，一般會有些速度快和快完結的反彈，故博短炒者要「非常之短線」。若要整個大勢轉變，便要待大環境消息，譬如中美關係轉好，內地經濟開始轉穩，才能重新走牛市，「但而家幾時見到底都暫時未知」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://down.57gif.com/down/1m/430251\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fdown.57gif.com%2Fdown%2F1m%2F430251&h=e2de89ab&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c6ca5e83b70161bc225bc4cc60a359659d2e9135","tid":875477,"uid":26773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-25T03:02:27.000Z","msg":"前兩日咪救左囉<br />\n第二日跌翻落黎咋麻<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6af09ba3a2660293f2cedbd68e1f73dba3267f99","tid":875477,"uid":12609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-25T03:04:40.000Z","msg":"個個星期都要救市 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 